summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of Twenty Dollars (20.00) from the general fund of the City of Seattle to pay the fourth annual premium on a re-delivery bond furnished by the Mayor in the suit of Peoples Pharmacy, a corporation, vs. C. L. Beckingham, et al, Cause No. 115533 of the files of the Superior Court for King County, Washington, and directing the City Comptroller to issue a warrant therefor.
